data.title: Katsucon
data.text:
We're working on updating all our info but for those asking #Katsucon24 is coming February 16-18, 2024!

Performer tryouts for our convention Dance events are OPEN! Email dance(at)katsucon.org with the subject line "DJ Demo" for details. Deadlines: #StationUnity until June 15th, and for #Katsucon until July 31st, 2023. pic.twitter.com/JwP8JBiGaK

#Volunteer to work with the Sakura Matsuri - Japanese Street Festival in downtown Washington, DC on April 15-16, 2023. Earn a free t-shirt, snacks, and the pride helping the largest 2-day celebration of Japanese culture in the US! Visit sakuramatsuri.org/volunteer/ @jas_wdc pic.twitter.com/QYeQsjBBRN

Anime fans are some of the most passionate and dedicated fans out there! Their love for the art form is contagious and inspiring. We love our fans and everything they’ve helped #Katsucon become!

That’s right we’re back and we getting things spun up as quickly as possible. Please check back in the next coming weeks for updates and information on Katsucon 2022 reopening.
